<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Turn More Leads Into Customers With This 8-Step B2B Sales Process</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="B2B Sales Process WordPress" class="wp-image-118820" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Process-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_60646750685d2" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’re likely under constant pressure to convert every </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/b2b-lead-generation-best-practices" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">B2B lead</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> you nurture—whether it’s a warm lead conducting product research or a cold lead who just wants your </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/evergreen-lead-magnet" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">lead magnet</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Sure, your job is to turn as many leads as possible into customers, but making B2B sales is a challenging task.</p>



<p>Considering the amount of money businesses invest in B2B products, they have to ensure your products help them achieve their goals. That’s why you’ll often have to interact and convince a company’s decision-makers before you land a B2B sale.</p>



<p>Since you already have a complex situation, you want to eliminate bottlenecks that can make the situation even tougher.</p>



<p>How can you achieve this? By creating an efficient B2B sales process.</p>



<p>In this guide, I’ll show you how to create a B2B sales process to close more sales and gain more profits for your business.</p>


