										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>9 Essential E-Commerce KPIs You Should Be Tracking</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-118790" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-KPIs-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_6062f22b77ff8" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">“Key performance indicator” (KPI) is a classic piece of marketing jargon.</span></p>
</div>






<p>But unlike a lot of marketing jargon (“low-hanging fruit,” anyone?) it actually means something.</p>



<p>KPIs allow you to chart performance toward your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/objectives-and-key-results" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">business objectives</a> through quantifiable data points or measurements. If you don’t have clearly defined KPIs, you’re effectively leaving things to chance.</p>



<p>Why are they so important?</p>



<p>Imagine your goal is to run a marathon. Would you set off running and hope you manage to reach 42 km? Or would you build a training plan built around key performance indicators, such as how many hours you spend doing cardio in the gym or how long it takes to recover between runs?</p>



<p>However naturally gifted you are, you’ll certainly see better results from the second approach—and e-commerce is no different.</p>



<p>Your goal might be to grow revenue by 20 percent year on year, but how are you going to get there? Rather than hoping it happens, far better to break down your overarching goal into KPIs that:</p>



<ul><li>Demonstrate whether you’re on the right track; and</li><li>Give you the opportunity to course-correct if things aren’t going as planned.</li></ul>



<p>With that in mind, here are nine vital e-commerce KPIs every brand should be tracking right now.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e9ff85a7a3a4" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Want More Conversion Optimization Tips?</h2>
