<h2 id="1"><strong>1. The eCommerce Fuel Podcast</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-1024x497.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118720" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image1-14.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The <a href="https://www.ecommercefuel.com/podcast/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">eCommerce fuel podcast</a> is a big player in the industry for a reason. Andrew Youderian, the podcast host, has a long history with e-commerce, dating back to 2007 when he launched his first c-commerce store selling CB radios.</p>



<p>The podcast covers all e-commerce topics, including brand-specific reports and current <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-trends" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">e-commerce trends.</a> There are over 400 episodes and 3 million total listens. </p>



<p>In addition to the podcast, eCommerce Fuel also has a community for e-tailers looking for extra support. Plus, they offer a business development program that helps e-commerce owners build partnerships and grow their online stores.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for: </strong>All listener types can enjoy this podcast. However, it’s good to have a basic understanding of e-commerce before tuning in.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. 2x eCommerce Podcast</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="565" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-1024x565.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118725" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-1024x565.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-300x165.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-768x423.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-1536x847.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-380x209.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-600x331.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-760x419.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-1440x794.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-91x50.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-740x408.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-220x121.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11-385x212.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image6-11.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The <a href="https://2xecommerce.com/podcast/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">2x eCommerce Podcast</a> is hosted by the e-commerce expert Kunle Campbell and is geared towards inspiring entrepreneurs and marketers in the retail industry. </p>



<p>You should check out this podcast if you’re interested in learning from various entrepreneurs, c-level executives, and marketers with a proven track record.</p>



<p>Each guest on the podcast shares how they doubled their e-commerce business and offers unique advice on how you can get started with your growth strategy in easy and digestible steps.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>2X podcast also hosts a Facebook community for people wanting to connect with like-minded entrepreneurs who’ve grown their online store to a seven or eight-figure business.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Intermediate to advanced knowledge. The language can be technical, so a deep understanding of e-commerce topics is required.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. My Wife Quit Her Job </strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="521" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-1024x521.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118728" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-1024x521.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-300x153.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-768x391.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-1536x781.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-380x193.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-600x305.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-760x387.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-1440x733.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-98x50.png 98w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-740x376.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-220x112.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11-385x196.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image5-11.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>If you’re thinking of starting an online business, <a href="https://mywifequitherjob.com/category/podcast/#:~:text=The%20MyWifeQuitHerJob%20podcast%20is%20a,that%20led%20to%20their%20success." target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The My Wife Quit Her Job</a> podcast is for you. </p>



<p>The host, Steve Chu, explains how his wife transitioned from a boring desk job to a successful online business. You’ll listen to a series of personal stories from entrepreneurs who are in the same boat as Steve’s wife.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This podcast differs from others because Steve is never afraid to ask the hard questions to understand the real strategies and details behind success.&nbsp;</p>



<p>My Wife Quit Her Job is an excellent option for beginners of e-commerce. (It might even convince you to quit your office job and start an e-commerce business.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> My Wife Quit Her Job covers everything from the very basics to more complex e-commerce topics. Beginners can easily understand the language and follow along, and experts can enjoy the podcast, too.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. E-Commerce Boost</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="596" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-1024x596.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118729" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-1024x596.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-768x447.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-1536x894.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-380x221.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-600x349.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-760x443.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-1440x838.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-740x431.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8-385x224.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image8-8.png 1872w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Sleeknote’s own <a href="https://sleeknote.com/e-commerce-boost" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">E-Commerce Boost</a> Podcast reviews some of the staple e-commerce marketing strategies for every industry. </p>



<p>If you’re struggling with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">cart abandonment</a>, SEO, or <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/best-email-marketing-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email marketing</a>, E-Commerce Boost can help you learn about these hyper-focused areas in e-commerce.</p>



<p>Plus, there are no long introductions, ads, or nonsense, making it easy to learn something new in just about 20 minutes. The interviews include e-commerce gurus like Dennis Yu, Roland Pokornyik, Julie Joyce, and more. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for: </strong>E-Commerce Boost is best for people who have basic industry knowledge. Knowing the basics will help you apply the marketing strategies discussed to your e-commerce store.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Future Commerce Podcast</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="525" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-1024x525.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118730" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-1024x525.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-300x154.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-768x394.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-1536x788.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-380x195.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-600x308.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-760x390.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-1440x738.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-98x50.png 98w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-740x379.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8-385x197.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image7-8.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Keeping up with future trends is crucial for your e-commerce business, and the <a href="https://futurecommerce.fm/future-commerce-podcast" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Future Commerce Podcast</a> can help you with that. </p>



<p>Every week, experts and startup founders join the hosts, Phillip Jackson and Brian Lange, to chat about where e-commerce is going.&nbsp;</p>



<p>It’s a podcast for innovators and founders who aren’t looking for the next <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/conversion-rate-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">conversion optimization</a> tip or how to execute a playbook. It’s for those who want to learn something deeper than CRO and PPC. </p>



<p>The podcast covers topics like new and upcoming e-commerce integrations, apps, automation tools, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">e-commerce statistics</a>, and more. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> To listen to this podcast, you should have an intermediate to advanced understanding of e-commerce topics.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. eCommerce FastLane</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="549" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-1024x549.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118732" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-1024x549.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-300x161.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-768x411.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-1536x823.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-380x204.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-600x321.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-760x407.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-1440x772.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-93x50.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-740x396.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-220x118.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15-385x206.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image2-15.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The <a href="https://ecommercefastlane.com/podcast/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">eCommerce FastLane</a> podcast aims to help e-commerce owners accelerate their business’s growth (specifically with Shopify). </p>



<p>The podcast is hosted by Steve Hutt, the startup founder and senior Merchant Success Manager at Shopify Plus.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Each episode interviews one of Shopify’s most successful e-commerce merchants about their marketing techniques and advice on how to grow an online store. Topics cover boutique e-commerce growth, subscriptions, recruiting, managing, and growing sales.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for: </strong>All listeners from different knowledge levels can easily follow along with the eCommerce FastLane podcast. </p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="7"><strong>7. eCommerce Lifestyle</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="567" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-1024x567.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118733" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-1024x567.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-1536x850.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-1440x797.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image4-11.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The <a href="https://www.ecommercelifestyle.com/courses/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">eCommerce Lifestyle</a> podcast aims at helping people find freedom through entrepreneurship. The podcast talks about the current global events, helping e-commerce owners know how to manage certain situations that affect their business. </p>



<p>The host, Anton Kraly, gets creative with his topics by asking unconventional questions, such as whether you should pay a supplier beforehand or not, the worst parts of dropshipping, things that will get you banned from Google, and so on.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This podcast’s topics can help fill in knowledge gaps you can use to grow your online business.</p>



<p>eCommerce Lifestyle also offers courses on specific areas, including Google ads for e-commerce, inbox funnels, dropshipping, and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/facebook-lead-ads" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Facebook</a>. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> The eCommerce Lifestyle is a great choice for every listener. It’s easy to follow along and covers topics that affect your e-commerce store, whether you’re a beginner or not. </p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="8"><strong>8. E-commerce Conversations by Practical E-commerce</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="533" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-1024x533.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118734" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-1024x533.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-300x156.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-768x400.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-1536x800.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-380x198.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-600x312.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-760x396.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-1440x750.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-740x385.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8-385x200.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image9-8.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The <a href="https://www.practicalecommerce.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Ecommerce Conversations by Practical Ecommerce</a> podcast is an excellent resource for e-commerce entrepreneurs looking to gain knowledge in leadership, management skills, product procurement, and placement. </p>



<p>If you enjoy hearing about what worked for other brands, this podcast is for you. Each week, Ecommerce Conversations release an episode hosted by Eric Bandholz, the founder and CEO of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/beardbrand-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Beardbrand</a>. They interview inspirational entrepreneurs and executives on the realities of online selling. Topics include finding success on Amazon, influencer marketing, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">list-building tools</a>, and more.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for: </strong>The Ecommerce Conversations podcast covers topics that are valuable to every listener’s knowledge level. It’s the perfect podcast to help inspire people to start an e-commerce store or find new ways to grow an existing one.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="9"><strong>9. The Fizzle Show</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="706" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-1024x706.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118735" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-1024x706.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-300x207.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-768x530.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-1536x1059.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-380x262.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-600x414.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-760x524.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-1440x993.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-711x490.png 711w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-220x152.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12-385x265.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image3-12.png 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><a href="https://fizzle.co/show/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Fizzle Show</a> is one of the oldest podcasts in the industry, dating back to 2013 when the first episode launched. They are now one of the biggest podcasts on the market, with 5 million downloads. </p>



<p>Entrepreneurs can tune in to this podcast for actionable business advice and tips from various industry experts. Podcast topics cover everything from specific tools to help your online business, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/success-stories" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">success stories</a>, life as a solo entrepreneur, and financial independence. </p>



<p>While most podcast episodes are free to listen to, you can become a Fizzle member to access a robust online community dedicated to helping entrepreneurs reach their business goals.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The membership also offers hours of training by Pat Flynn from <a href="https://www.smartpassiveincome.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Smart Passive Income</a> and Dana Shultz from <a href="https://minimalistbaker.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Minimalist Baker</a>. There are also courses, weekly coaching sessions, and access to a Facebook community. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> This podcast is aimed at listeners who are hungry to grow their business, whether you’re a new e-commerce owner looking to expand your knowledge or an experienced entrepreneur looking to boost a specific part of your business.</p>
</div></div>


