										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>10 Proven B2B Sales Pitch Examples to Inspire Your Own</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="B2B Sales Pitch Examples WordPress" class="wp-image-118683" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/B2B-Sales-Pitch-Examples-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_605c78d09b688" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">B2B sales pitches can make or break deals.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Get your pitch right and you get the business. But get it wrong and you’ll risk losing a customer.</p>



<p>Think of a sales pitch as your verbal business card that should be solid enough to make an excellent first impression. It must be concise and crisp to ensure the listener believes what you want them to.</p>



<p>But here’s where things get tricky: Our brains are wired to resist sales messages. So you need to nail down your sales pitch before meeting the potential client.</p>



<p>Luckily, there are a few tried-and-tested formulas that can help you come up with winning B2B sales pitches.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Read on as I discuss the best sales pitch strategies, along with foolproof B2B sales pitch examples that’ll make your pitching game stronger.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e9ff85a7a3a4" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Want More Conversion Optimization Tips?</h2>
