					<description><![CDATA[<p>Everything You Need to Know About E-Commerce NPS Conversion Rate Optimization Keeping customers around means they’ll keep buying from you, giving you a steady income stream. That’s why churn rate is such a crucial metric to measure for your online store. Although churn rate is typically used by SaaS companies, many e-commerce businesses started adopting [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-nps">Everything You Need to Know About E-Commerce NPS</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sleeknote.com">Sleeknote</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Everything You Need to Know About E-Commerce NPS</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="E-Commerce NPS WordPress" class="wp-image-118673" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-NPS-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_605c5303afa77" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Customers are important, but so is </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-retention-emails" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">customer retention</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Keeping customers around means they’ll keep buying from you, giving you a steady income stream. That’s why churn rate is such a crucial metric to measure for your online store.</p>



<p>Although churn rate is typically used by SaaS companies, many e-commerce businesses started adopting this metric to measure <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">customer loyalty</a> over a longer time period.</p>



<p>To <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/reduce-churn" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">reduce churn</a> and improve loyalty, you should keep an eye on your Net Promoter Score (NPS) and actively work on improving this score.</p>



<p>In this guide, we’ll cover all the basics of e-commerce NPS and how you can implement it to improve customer satisfaction.</p>



<p>Let&#8217;s begin.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e9ff85a7a3a4" class="block-content-upgrade">
