<h2><strong>Over to You</strong></h2>



<p>That was everything you need to know about e-commerce NPS.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Keeping an eye on your NPS can help you understand your target customers better, know their likes and dislikes, and improve any shortcomings and flaws in your online store.</p>



<p>You can&#8217;t expect overnight change, but by actively tracking NPS, you can eventually create an army of loyal customers, leading to more revenue in the future.<br><em>Are you using NPS surveys on your e-commerce site? Share your experience below.</em></p>
