<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>10 E-Commerce Trends You Can’t Ignore in 2021</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="E-Commerce Trends WordPress" class="wp-image-118654" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Trends-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_605b2783911f9" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">E-commerce is a highly dynamic niche.</span></p>
</div>






<p>The rules, people’s preferences and buying patterns, and the tech is constantly changing.</p>



<p>Staying up-to-date with these dynamic patterns is essential for your sales—especially when the competition is off the roof with millions of buyers shopping online instead of physically visiting malls and storefronts.</p>



<p>So what is the new normal for e-commerce? And what should you do to make sure your business thrives?</p>



<p>Read on as I go over the 10 crucial e-commerce trends for 2021.</p>


