										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Follow These E-Commerce Survey Best Practices to Get More Feedback</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-1024x437.jpg" alt="E-Commerce Survey Best Practices WordPress" class="wp-image-118516" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/E-Commerce-Survey-Best-Practices-WordPress.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_605318b622535" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every e-commerce brand wants to have happy customers. In fact, every brand wants to have happy customers, full stop.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Once this aim was more of a vague notion than a specific priority, but today customer experience has become the <a href="https://www.superoffice.com/blog/customer-experience-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">number one focus for business leaders</a>. Here’s what they said when asked for their business priorities over the coming five years:</p>



<ol><li>Customer experience (chosen by 45.9 percent of respondents)</li><li>Product (33.6 percent)</li><li>Pricing (20.5 percent)</li></ol>



<p>I know what you’re thinking. “Customer experience is more important than my product? Surely that can’t be right?”</p>



<p>This shouldn’t be so surprising. <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/satisfaction-guarantees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Happy customers</a> are happy for a reason. Maybe you delighted them with a surprise discount, a silky-smooth buying process, or lightning-fast delivery.</p>



<p>In other words, they feel happy because of something you did, and they’re prepared to <a href="https://www.pwc.com/us/en/services/consulting/library/consumer-intelligence-series/future-of-customer-experience.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">reward you for it</a>. They’ll pay up to 16 percent more for your product, and they’ll be more loyal to your brand, too.</p>



<p>To improve your customer experience and make them even more satisfied, you first need to understand how happy they are right now.</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-survey-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">E-commerce surveys</a> are one of the best ways to do this. With that in mind, here are 9 best practices to help you create effective, insightful surveys.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e9ff85a7a3a4" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
